snippet.title: PlayStation - Simple Character 2000 Series Vol 01 - Kidou Senshi Gundam   The Gunjin Shougi (2001)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
The Gunjin Shogi: Kidou Senshi Gundam is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Amedio and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2001.
